      "title": "Reruns from 29th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Electricity Board of Sri Lanka has announced that the first generator that suddenly failed at Nuraicholai Thermal Power Station will be able to be connected to the national power grid from next Monday (29).",
        "According to this, 300 MW of electricity will be included in the national power grid. (R)"
      ],
